            </ul></div><div class="d_post_content_main ">    <div class="p_content ">        <div class="save_face_bg_hidden save_face_bg_0"><a class="save_face_card"></a></div>                <cc>            <div id="post_content_59444365" class="d_post_content j_d_post_content ">            <br>　　目前，中国科研单位的课题（项目）来源主要有4类。第一，科技主管部门根据科技发展规划和计划提出的指令性和指导性课题（项目），称为科技发展规划和计划内项目，包括各级科技计划和基金项目。其中国家级的科技计划包括&quot;国家高技术研究发展计划（即863计划）&quot;、&quot;<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60Xyr1Cfw79rAir7AocARkkXZSTiMtP0/5KNniM6cLn7IG3iDXC86nFt6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayMhMZgfTf+uS"  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'国家科技攻关计划'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">国家科技攻关计划</a>&quot;、&quot;<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60Xyr1Cfw79rCI6DPUkK53zlRuziwBlRgtOpfVGEvOY1OGOYLW27dcxoM6xoMDb1ROBt4g1wvOpxbel8om1RYJOH2yzIMrVIOWeEODjt9EYvEgLVY0sdTYyWPCuOEbRGsjITGYH03/rkg=="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'国家重点基础研究发展计划'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">国家重点基础研究发展计划</a>（即<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63XzcATLUaKFBnWtxDR4lYQImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQsUcyHzEJDzubAG+4Cm4FSU0="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'973计划'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">973计划</a>）&quot;、&quot;基础研究重大项目前期研究专项&quot;、&quot;<a href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63Rbwsa2z5x2KIVhRLMqe6cgbeINcLzqcW3pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrIyExmB9N/65I="  class="ps_cb" target="_blank" onclick="$.stats.track(0, 'nlp_ps_word',{obj_name:'星火计划'});$.stats.track('Pb_content_wordner','ps_callback_statics')">星火计划</a>&quot;、&quot;